reviews.text: I had her for freshman MWH. Shes a pretty good teacher and if you do the work youll get an A/A- easily. I dont like her very much anyway, maybe its bc I have 1st block, but shes just boring and kinda annoying. Her voice bothers me, but shes still pretty easy.

She def has fav students. participate a lot and she wont go hard on you. ik this bc all her favs get better grades when I DID THE SAME THING AND GOT A LOWER GRADE. do the pretests and use flashcards. most the qs In the pretest r qs of the tests. STUDY UR MAPS ALAAAAATTTT OF THAT IN THE TESTS. she gives a lot of notes with quizzes after (mostly 5qs).

She’s very understanding... although to a good grade on her Tests, DO THE PRE TESTS!!! You won’t receive a good grade without doing the pre- tests, also do the notes, she includes them in many future lessons, trust me!!!
Shes a good teacher, not super easy but definitely manageable to get an A. She goee at a good pace, and you’ll learn a lot
